    • update

      public Node update(Node node, int from, int to, byte[] insertedContent)
      Description copied from interface: NodeService
      Update the content in the range [from, to[. The content must be inserted in any case. i.e. : "hello world" -> update(0, 0, "inserted ") -> "inserted hello world" : "hello world" -> update(0, 5, "inserted ") -> "inserted world"
      Specified by:
      update in interface NodeService
      Parameters:
      node - Node to update (must be a file).
      from - Beginning index of the text to update.
      to - Last index of the text to update (Not included).
      insertedContent - Content to insert.
      Returns:
      The node that has been updated.
